&lt;p&gt;I implemented/improved the following:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;PDSimpleFont#drawString now uses glyphs for rendering&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;unencoded values are used for the rendering of CID encoded fonts&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;introduced a new value to povide the information if the AWT-font was substituted or not&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
